{"tid":536223,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意咗個做七仔既女仔 可以點做？","createTime":"2018-01-21T15:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T16:26:51.000Z","uid":37822,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"02043642e417887302eeb84a683565cb9e78ed59","tid":536223,"uid":37822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"我每日都會係同一間七仔度買飲品 <br />\n有一日見到呢個女仔就覺得一見鍾情<br />\n有日見唔到佢係度收錢就好失落 <br />\n突然佢出現係我面前個心就卜卜咁跳<br />\n<br />\n我每日都做顧客既 可以點樣識佢 同佢做多啲溝通了解下佢 <br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/231123_3fcd6e37e19ac54d9871d10f61b3ac48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F231123_3fcd6e37e19ac54d9871d10f61b3ac48.png&h=d87b4903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36c8328aa84ee2a2483736cbeace5df0d9cee7e2","tid":536223,"uid":5044,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"你估真係買多啲儲印花 就可以換條女返屋企咩<br />\n你係靚仔嘅話條女就係贈品唔係換購品"},{"pid":"ab30783e07cc5518b84000c4fb7323a050aba21a","tid":536223,"uid":148201,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"直接話:你幾錢"},{"pid":"fc9ad8e8599e646e7850bd6fc9cddb814b44f2e0","tid":536223,"uid":27482,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"同佢做同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e4181c5a459d4d669187f25d75b973bf21aa86","tid":536223,"uid":123820,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"靚仔: 買兩支野飲行過去比錢 拎電話出黎好似交電話費咁 開打電話個UI出黎 問佢可唔可以識佢/接佢收工食糖水之類 之後留低一支野飲請佢飲<br />\n<br />\nPLAN B: 買2支可樂, 係其中一支可樂個樽下半部度用黑筆寫電話Number, 比完錢話請佢飲<br />\n<br />\n毒撚/樣衰: 番去照下鏡唔好ff咁多"},{"pid":"fe6e6f8386a42c1d93bfaff3a0094ce75b8c6bb1","tid":536223,"uid":37822,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"d3e4181c5a459d4d669187f25d75b973bf21aa86","tid":536223,"uid":123820,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58